fields.name: The Cheese Almighty
fields.description: An assortment of several delicious cheeses including Cheddar, Mozerella, Parmesan and Feta, served on a rich tomato sauce base with extra thick crust topped with parmesan.

fields.name: Ai Broccoli
fields.description: Another Italian classic!! Crispy and chewy base goes with our rich tomato sauce, Mozzarella in abundance on top and garnished with Broccoli, Garlic, Chili peppers and Oregano.

fields.name: Calabrese
fields.description: Tomato sauce, Parmigian Reggiano (Parmesan), Tuna, Olives, Capers, Garlic, Onion, Hot Calabrian chili peppers

fields.name: Capricciosca
fields.description: Tomato sauce, Mozzarella, Mushrooms, Artichokes, Cooked ham, Olives, Olive oil

fields.name: Caprina
fields.description: Tomato sauce, Creamy Goat’s cheese, Other ingredients include the following: Arugula, Chili peppers, Baby spinach leafes, Olives, Olive oil sat on a thin based crispy crust.

fields.name: Margherita
fields.description: The Italian Classic. Our super soft, thick dough compliment this lushest rich tomato sauce, a heap of Mozzarella complimented with fresh Olive oil and topped with Basil leaves

fields.name: Napoletana
fields.description: One of Italy's finest creations! Our thin, crispy base has our trademark rich tomato sauce, topped with Mozzarella and added Anchovies complimented with traditional Olive oil.

fields.name: Prosciutto
fields.description: Tomato sauce, Mozzarella, Prosciutto (Italian ham)

fields.name: Romana
fields.description: Tomato sauce, Mozzarella, Anchovies, Oregano, Olive oil

fields.name: 2L Coke
fields.description: 2 Litre bottle of Original Coca Cola.

fields.name: Fries
fields.description: Rustic fries, double cooked for a crispy finish. Check out our sauces to accompany your delicious hand cooked fries.

fields.name: Hawaian
fields.description: Classic Hawaian pizza made up of tangy pineapple chunks and crispy chopped ham on a thick crust with rich tomato sauce, a generous topping of cheeses and a dusting of basil.

fields.name: Texas BBQ
fields.description: Texan style BBQ sauce covered chicken strips with chunks of ham, pepperoni on a thick crust covered in lashings of more sweet, sticky, BBQ sauce and topped with two cheeses.

fields.name: 2L Fanta
fields.description: 2 Litre bottle of Original Fanta Orange.

fields.name: Pulled Pork
fields.description: Crispy thick base with a rich layer of tomato, cheese then a pile of juicy, sweet, pulled pork.

fields.name: Hot N Spicy
fields.description: Jalapenos, chopped chillies and chilli sauce make this a mouth burner!! But with a delish thing crust and mountains of cheese is hot n delicious!

fields.name: Texas BBQ with 2 x Fries & 2L Coca Cola
fields.description: Large Texas BBQ pizza (sticky, BBQ sauce on a crispy base topped with two cheeses) and two side order of fries and a 2L bottle of Coca Cola. 2 x Dips.

fields.name: Margerita with 2 x Fries & 2L Fanta
fields.description: Our super soft, thick dough compliment this lushest rich tomato sauce, a heap of Mozzarella. 2 x Sides of our in house Fries and a 2 Litre bottle of Fanta.2 x Dips.

fields.name: Dips Assortment
fields.description: Garlic Mayo, Ketchup, BBQ and Sweet Chilli

fields.name: Farmhouse
fields.description: A bounty of rustic toppings include, Mushroom, chicken pieces, ham and sweetcorn. Deliciously smothered in two types of cheese.

fields.name: Super Meaty
fields.description: Chunks of ham, spicy peperoni, beef and topped with peperoni! This deep crust is crunchy and finished with cheese on a bed of rich beefy, tomato sauce.
